0at%206.45%20pm.%20Again%2C%20the%20doctors'%20demand%20for%20live-streaming%20and%20officials'%20refusal%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20roadblock.%20The%20medicos%20waited%20outside%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20home%20in%20the%20rain.%20They%20demanded%20that%C2%A0they%20be%20allowed%20to%20videograph%20the%20meeting.%20The%20state%20government%20refused%20this%20and%20said%20it%20would%20record%20the%20meeting%20and%20the%20recording%20would%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20doctors%20later%20because%20the%20matter%20is%20sub-judice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20came%20out%20and%20invited%20the%20doctors%20inside.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20trust%20me%2C%20I%20won't%20mislead%20you.%20Even%20if%20you%20do%20not%20attend%20the%20meeting%2C%20at%20least%20have%20a%20cup%20of%20tea.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20said%20the%20doctors%20are%20%26quot%3Binsulting%26quot%3B%20her.%20The%20doctors%20stressed%20that%20they%20wanted%20the%20recording.%20She%20then%20said%20I%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20accept%20all%20your%20demands%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Later%20that%20night%2C%20the%20doctors%20decided%20to%20join%20the%20meeting%20but%20state%20minister%20Chandrima%20Bhattacharya%20and%20chief%20secretary%20Manoj%20Pant%20told%20them%20it%20was%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726472640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F3hjl4jho_mamata_625x300_16_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freaching-out-for-fifth-final-time-mamata-banerjee-invites-doctors-for-meet-6576220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BReaching%20Out%20For%20Fifth%2C%20Final%20Time%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Invites%20Doctors%20For%20Meet%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freaching-out-for-fifth-final-time-mamata-banerjee-invites-doctors-for-meet-6576220%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampU