20with%20modern%20amenities%20and%20safety%20features.%20We%20take%20a%20look%20at%20Vande%20Metro's%20route%2C%20fare%2C%20schedule%20and%20stoppages%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fvande-metro-flag-off-pm-modi-new-indian-railways-train-launch-today-check-fare-bhuj-ahmedabad-route-schedule-stoppages-top-features%2Farticleshow%2F113384595.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20BJP%20Faces%20Three%20Big%20Challenges%20In%20Haryana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3vn1d678_haryana_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20final%20date%20for%20nominations%20closing%20in%20Haryana%2C%20frenzied%20campaigning%20has%20begun%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20will%20vote%20on%20October%205.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20grappling%20with%20a%20triple%20anti-incumbency%20situation%20and%20is%20fighting%20an%20uphill%20battle%20in%20an%20election%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20considered%20the%20favourite%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20trends%20in%20both%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections%20are%20not%20favourable%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20demonstrate%20that%20no%20election%20in%20India%20is%20a%20foregone%20conclusion%20until%20the%20last%20vote%20is%20counted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20September%2012%2C%20there%20were%201%2C745%20candidates%20in%20the%20fray%20-%20about%2020%20per%20seat%20-%20with%20the%20final%20date%20for%20withdrawal%20set%20for%20September%2016.%20The%20ticket%20distribution%20has%20sparked%20rebellion%2C%20particularly%20within%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20has%20faced%20less%20dissent.%20Many%20candidates%20who%20were%20denied%20tickets%20have%20filed%20nominations%20as%20independents.%20The%20BJP%20has%20replaced%2015%20MLAs%2C%20while%20Congress%20has%20not%20re-nominated%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20five%20main%20parties%20contesting%20-%20Congress%2C%20BJP%2C%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal-Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party-Azad%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party-approximately%2015%20candidates%20from%20smaller%20parties%20and%20independents%20have%20filed%20their%20papers.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20parties%20will%20attempt%20to%20persuade%20rebels%20to%20withdraw%20their%20nominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20is%20experiencing%20several%20competing%20and%20parallel%20trends.%20No%20party%20has%20won%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20state%20since%20its%20inception%20in%201966.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20replaced%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20just%20before%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20has%20never%20lost%20an%20election%20when%20employing%20this%20strategy%20-%20evident%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Tripura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20faces%20anti-incumbency%20on%20three%20fronts%3A%20the%20central%20government%2C%20the%20state%20government%20and%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20and%20local%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20level%20of%20anti-incumbency%20partially%20manifested%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%20Discontent%20among%20voters%20arose%20from%20the%20mishandling%20of%20farmers'%20protests.%2061%25%20of%20farmers%20(up%2020%20percentage%20points%2C%20or%20pp)%20supported%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20with%20many%20belonging%20to%20the%20influential%20Jat%20community%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20party's%20troubles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20were%20displeased%20with%20the%20BJP's%20inaction%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20despite%20sexual%20harassment%20charges%20by%20wrestlers.%20As%20many%20as%2049%25%20of%20women%20(up%2020%20pp)%20voted%20against%20the%20BJP.%20Notably%2C%2020%25%20of%20the%20Olympic%20team%20representing%20India%20in%20Paris%20hailed%20from%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouth%20protests%20against%20the%20new%20Agniveer%20Scheme%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20went%20unaddressed%20by%20the%20BJP.%2011%25%20of%20soldiers%20in%20the%20Indian%20army%20come%20from%20Haryana%2C%20and%2047%25%20of%20voters%20aged%2018-25%20years%20supported%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20issues%20led%20to%20significant%20losses%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Haryana.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20won%20all%2010%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20saw%20its%20tally%20dropping%20to%20five%20seats%20in%202024%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20winning%20the%20other%20five.%20The%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20decreased%20by%2012%20pp%2C%20while%20Congress%20gained%2016%20pp.%20The%20BJP%20led%20in%2044%20assembly%20segments%20(down%2035%20from%202019)%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20led%20in%2046%20(up%2036).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20Level%20Anti-Incumbency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20level%20of%20anti-incumbency%20is%20directed%20at%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20state%20government.%20The%20BJP%20replaced%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20just%20six%20months%20before%20the%20state%20polls.%20Khattar%20was%20the%20face%20of%20the%20BJP's%20anti-dominant%20caste%20politics%20strategy%2C%20which%20had%20previously%20succeeded%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20after%20the%202014%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20nominated%20OBC%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20instead%20of%20someone%20from%20the%20Jat%20community%2C%20failing%20to%20placate%20the%20influential%20caste.%20Haryana%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20unemployment%20rates%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20CMIE%2C%20and%20an%20inflation%20rate%20of%204.12%25%20for%20August%202024%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20all-India%20average%20of%203.65%25.%20Unemployment%20and%20price%20rises%20were%20top%20issues%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20criticised%20the%20BJP%20government%20for%20a%20significant%20rise%20in%20crime.%20The%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20report%20for%202022%20shows%20a%20troubling%2017.6%25%20increase%20in%20criminal%20cases%2C%20totalling%202.43%20lakh%20cases.%20Haryana%2C%20after%20Delhi%2C%20has%20the%20second-highest%20number%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocal%20MLA%20Anti-Incumbency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20level%20of%20anti-incumbency%20is%20against%20the%20local%20MLAs.%20In%20state%20elections%2C%20the%20local%20candidate%20is%20crucial%2C%20as%2036%25%20of%20voters%20considered%20this%20the%20primary%20factor%20in%20the%202014%20state%20polls%2C%20according%20to%20a%20CSDS%20post-poll%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20dropped%2015%20MLAs%20and%20changed%20the%20seats%20for%20three%20others%2C%20including%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%2037%25%20denial%2Freplacement%20ratio.%20New%20candidates%20have%20been%20fielded%20in%2057%20seats%2C%20nearly%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20assembly%2C%20to%20dilute%20local%20anti-incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20has%20a%20history%20of%20punishing%20incumbent%20MLAs.%20In%20the%202019%20state%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20repeated%2034%20of%20its%2047%20sitting%20MLAs%2C%20and%20half%20of%20them%20lost.%20The%20Congress%20repeated%20all%20its%20MLAs%2C%20with%20half%20also%20losing.%20Out%20of%20the%2049%20repeated%20MLAs%20by%20Congress%20and%20BJP%2C%20half%20lost%20their%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20worrisome%20trend%20for%20the%20BJP%20is%20its%20tendency%20to%20lose%20seats%20and%20vote%20share%20in%20state%20elections%20held%20after%20general%20elections.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20BJP%20led%20in%2052%20assembly%20segments%20in%20the%202014%20general%20elections%2C%20which%20dropped%20to%2047%20in%20the%20state%20polls%20held%20six%20months%20later.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20party%20led%20in%2079%20assembly%20segments%2C%20which%20fell%20to%2040%20in%20the%20state%20polls.%20Its%20Lok%20Sabha%20vote%20share%20of%2058%25%20reduced%20to%2037%25%20in%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20currently%20favoured%20to%20win%20Haryana%20according%20to%20initial%20surveys.%20However%2C%20with%20elections%20becoming%20increasingly%20complex%20and%20pollsters%20having%20struggled%20in%20both%20the%202023%20state%20and%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20no%20election%20in%20India%20is%20a%20sure%20thing%20until%20the%20last%20vote%20is%20counted.%20BJP%20supporters%20hope%20for%20an%20upset%20similar%20to%20the%202023%20results%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20or%20a%20hung%20verdict%20due%20to%20smaller%20parties'%20influence.%20A%20fascinating%20contest%20is%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726467960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3vn1d678_haryana_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbjps-haryana-challenges-are-mounting-6575971%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20grappling%20with%20a%20triple%20anti-incumbency%20situation%20and%20is%20fighting%20an%20uphill%20battle%20in%20an%20election%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20considered%20the%20favourite%20to%20win.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbjps-haryana-challe