k%20snake.%26quot%3B%20Her%20comment%20came%20during%20the%20inauguration%20of%20JJP%20candidate%20Krishna%20Gangwa's%20election%20office%20in%20Adampur%2C%20just%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Mr%20Dhanak%2C%20a%20former%20JJP%20leader%20who%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20recently%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20gave%20love%20and%20respect%20to%20Anoop%20but%20even%20a%20two-faced%20snake%20is%20better%20than%20him.%20At%20least%20a%20snake%20knows%20which%20way%20it%20will%20bite.%20God%20gave%20Anoop%20the%20face%20of%20a%20black%20snake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElected%20as%20a%20JJP%20candidate%20in%20the%202019%20Haryana%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Dhanak%20served%20as%20a%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20the%20coalition%20government%20between%20the%20JJP%20and%20BJP.%20His%20loyalty%20to%20the%20Chautala%20family%2C%20particularly%20Ajay%20Chautala%20and%20Dushyant%20Chautala%2C%20initially%20appeared%20steadfast.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20support%20Ajay%20Chautala%20when%20the%20JJP%20was%20formed%20in%20December%202018%2C%20following%20a%20split%20in%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20surprising%20move%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Dhanak%20left%20the%20JJP%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20fielded%20him%20as%20its%20candidate%20for%20the%20Uklana%20constituency%20in%20Hisar%20district.%20His%20defection%2C%20along%20with%20that%20of%20former%20JJP%20leaders%20Ram%20Kumar%20Gautam%20and%20Jogi%20Ram%20Sihag%2C%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20political%20boost%20for%20the%20BJP.%20The%20ruling%20party%20in%20Haryana%20welcomed%20these%20defectors%2C%20strengthening%20its%20position%20ahead%20of%20the%20October%205%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaina%20Chautala%20also%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20with%20how%20the%20JJP's%20former%20allies%20have%20aligned%20themselves%20with%20their%20political%20opponents.%20Naina%20Chautala%20added%20that%20the%20JJP%20had%20worked%20to%20uplift%20backwards%20and%20scheduled%20caste%20leaders%20like%20Mr%20Dhanak%2C%20offering%20them%20respect%20and%20leadership%20opportunities.%20%26quot%3BWe%20spared%20no%20effort%20to%20give%20respect%20to%20SC%20and%20backward%20classes.%20We%20also%20sent%20Anoop%20Dhanak%20as%20the%20state%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Her%20tone%2C%20however%2C%20shifted%20as%20she%20accused%20Mr%20Dhanak%20of%20betrayal%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20written%20on%20anyone's%20forehead%20that%20it%20will%20stab%20them%20in%20the%20back.%20When%20someone%20stands%20with%20us%2C%20he%20is%20ours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20JJP%20supporters%20to%20campaign%20against%20Ms%20Dhanak%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20relatives%20in%20Uklana%2C%20then%20you%20must%20work%20to%20ask%20for%20votes%20against%20him.%20Do%20the%20work%20so%20that%20he%20knows%20what%20happens%20when%20he%20stabs%20the%20Devi%20Lal%20family%20in%20the%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Naina%20Chautala's%20controversial%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Dhanak%20was%20quoted%20by%20Amar%20Ujala%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20Have%20served%20their%20family%20for%2020-25%20years%20and%20have%20given%20Naina%20Chautala%20respect%20as%20a%20mother.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20say%20my%20poverty%20should%20not%20have%20been%20ridiculed.%20I%20did%20not%20break%20the%20party%20but%20resigned%20after%205%20years.%20My%20complexion%20is%20the%20same%20today%20as%20it%20was%2020%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20for%20Haryana's%2090%20Assembly%20seats%20will%20be%20held%20on%20October%205%2C%20with%20results%20to%20be%20declared%20on%20October%208.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726460760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fsq4qvfj8_naina-chautala-anoop-dhanak-_625x300_16_September_24.