.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221818%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20satellite%20image%20of%20Trump%20Golf%20Club%20at%20West%20Palm%20Beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e7a015d17aa3c7b2b2bd3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20satellite%20image%20of%20Trump%20Golf%20Club%20at%20West%20Palm%20Beach%20indicates%20the%20location%20of%20holes%205%20and%206%2C%20where%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Maps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20blind%20spots%2C%20James%20added%20that%20the%20Secret%20Service%20would%20never%20shut%20down%20an%20entire%20golf%20course%20%E2%80%94%20even%20for%20a%20sitting%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20always%20practical%20to%20shut%20down%20things%20like%20abutting%20roadways%20%E2%80%94%20that%20could%20get%20very%20extensive.%20And%20then%20you%20start%20to%20interrupt%20commerce%20and%20traffic%20just%20for%20the%20president%20golfing%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20it%20gets%20tough%20to%20justify%20something%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20former%20agent%20said%20a%20security%20detail%20would%20set%20a%20perimeter%20around%20where%20the%20president%20is%20golfing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20time%20in%20the%20Secret%20Service%2C%20James%20said%20that%20his%20team%20usually%20had%20an%20agent%20walk%20out%20one%20hole%20ahead%20along%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Btrailing%20element%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20nobody%20could%20sneak%20up%20behind%20the%20president.%20James%20said%20there%20was%20also%20a%20team%20that%20would%20be%20in%20proximity%20to%20the%20president%20in%20case%20he%20needed%20to%20be%20grabbed%20and%20evacuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agent%20who%20was%20out%20ahead%20who%20saw%20it%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20exactly%20what%20he%20or%20she%20was%20supposed%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3