t%E2%80%99s%20faces%20and%20the%20strain%20it%20put%20on%20our%20entire%20community.%20This%20crisis%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20fragility%20of%20our%20water%20resources%20and%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20better%20management%20and%20understanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20incident%20Dr%20Chorol%20recalls%20is%20from%20her%20undergraduate%20days%20when%20she%20visited%20her%20ancestral%20village%20called%20Skumpata%20(Lingshet)%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302635%2Fladakh-ministry-of-education-score-new-heights-role-of-dedicated-teachers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELadakh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20about%2080%20km%20from%20Leh%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20ingenious%20traditional%20water%20management%20systems%20our%20ancestors%20had%20developed%20%E2%80%94%20the%20intricate%20network%20of%20channels%20and%20storage%20ponds%20that%20had%20sustained%20life%20in%20this%20harsh%20landscape%20for%20centuries.%20However%2C%20I%20also%20noticed%20how%20these%20systems%20were%20under%20threat%20from%20changing%20climate%20patterns%20and%20modernisation.%20It%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20importance%20of%20bridging%20traditional%20knowledge%20with%20modern%20scientific%20approaches%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-500x625.webp%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Lobzang%20Chorol%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-500x625.webp%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-240x300.webp%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-150x188.webp%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445.webp%20736w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365885%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Lobzang%20Chorol%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20this%20fascination%20and%20concern%20that%20motivated%20her%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20cold%20desert%E2%80%99s%20water%20systems%20to%20pursue%20her%20PhD%20at%20IIT-ISM%20(Indian%20School%20of%20Mines)%2C%20Dhanbad.%20Under%20the%20mentorship%20of%20Professor%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20a%20leading%20expert%20in%20the%20field%2C%20she%20closely%20studied%20the%20groundwater%20systems%20in%20Leh%20town.%20Spanning%20six%20years%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20her%20research%20finally%20culminated%20in%20the%20completion%20of%20her%20thesis%20earlier%20this%20year.%20(You%20can%20find%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FLobzang-Chorol%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20times%20when%20the%20challenges%20seemed%20overwhelming%20%E2%80%94%20from%20people%20unwilling%20to%20give%20their%20borewell%20water%20samples%20to%20collecting%20secondary%20baseline%20data%20and%20the%20emotional%20weight%20of%20seeing%20the%20deterioration%20of%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20water%20resources%20firsthand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20every%20time%20I%20felt%20discouraged%2C%20I%20remembered%20the%20faces%20of%20my%20family%20and%20community%20back%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20depending%20on%20this%20precious%20resource.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20academic%20research%3B%20it%20was%20about%20the%20lives%20and%20futures%20of%20real%20people.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20earning%20a%20degree%3B%20it%20was%20about%20securing%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20Ladakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeh%E2%80%99s%20invisible%20network%20of%20underground%20aquifers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeh%20is%20a%20town%20nestled%20in%20the%20rain%20shadow%20area%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312359%2Fscientist-innovates-solar-hamam-warm-water-heater-for-thousands-in-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emighty%20Himalayas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20receiving%20barely%20100%20mm%20of%20annual%20rainfall.%20Life%20in%20this%20high-altitude%20desert%20thrives%20against%20all%20odds%2C%20thanks%20to%20an%20invisible%20network%20of%20underground%20aquifers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20aquifers%20are%20essentially%20natural%20underground%20reservoirs%20formed%20in%20the%20porous%20layers%20of%20rock%20and%20sediment%20beneath%20Leh.%20They%20are%20recharged%20primarily%20by%20snowmelt%20from%20surrounding%20mountains%2C%20glacial%20melt%20from%20nearby%20glaciers%2C%20limited%20annual%20rainfall%2C%20and%20infiltration%20from%20rivers%20and%20streams.%20This%20recharge%20process%20is%20heavily%20influenced%20by%20seasonal%20patterns%2C%20with%20most%20occurring%20during%20the%20warmer%20months%20when%20snow%20and%20glaciers%20melt%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Chorol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20aquifers%20act%20as%20a%20natural%20storage%20and%20filtration%20system%2C%20holding%20water%20that%20percolates%20through%20the%20ground%20and%20releasing%20it%20slowly%20over%20time.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20groundwater%20maintains%20a%20relatively%20stable%20temperature%2C%20which%20can%20be%20beneficial%20for%20both%20ecosystems%20and%20human%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20920px)%20100vw%2C%20920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t