0smart%20technologies%2C%20advanced%20control%20systems%2C%20and%20IoT-enabled%20platforms%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20create%20a%20seamless%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20scalable%20energy%20infrastructure%20that%20supports%20the%20global%20transition%20to%20greener%20and%20more%20sustainable%20transportation%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20the%20fast%20charger%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Vivek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20development%20of%20Plugzmart%E2%80%99s%2060kW%20DC%20Fast%20Charger%20began%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20other%20DC%20charger%20projects%20with%20a%20dedicated%20focus%20on%20high-power%20charging%20solutions%20initiated%20about%20two%20years%20ago.%20We%20went%20through%20approximately%20three%20prototypes%20before%20arriving%20at%20the%20current%20model.%20Each%20prototype%20underwent%20rigorous%20testing%20to%20refine%20efficiency%2C%20power%20management%2C%20and%20safety%20standards.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20these%20two%20years%2C%20there%20were%20multiple%20challenges%20they%20had%20to%20overcome%20in%20the%20development%20process.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20primary%20challenge%20was%20designing%20a%20proprietary%20controller%20card%20that%20would%20seamlessly%20handle%20high-speed%20charging%20while%20maintaining%20a%20compact%20size%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founders%20Vivek%20Samynathan%20and%20Ragavendra%20Ravichandran%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365377%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECo-founders%20Vivek%20Samynathan%20and%20Ragavendra%20Ravichandran%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20a%20controller%20card%20do%3F%20%E2%80%9CThe%20controller%20card%20manages%20power%20distribution%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20safety%20protocols%20during%20charging.%20It%20monitors%20critical%20parameters%2C%20such%20as%20voltage%2C%20current%2C%20and%20temperature%20to%20prevent%20overheating%20and%20overcharging%2C%20ensuring%20safe%20operation.%20The%20controller%20also%20enables%20intelligent%20load%20management%2C%20balancing%20power%20across%20multiple%20charging%20points%2C%20enabling%20simultaneous%20charging%20of%20multiple%20EVs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ragavendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchieving%20efficient%20heat%20dissipation%20at%20such%20high%20power%20levels%2C%20minimising%20energy%20losses%2C%20and%20preventing%20component%20damage%20were%20critical%20challenges%20too.%20We%20also%20focused%20on%20ensuring%20compatibility%20with%20multiple%20vehicle%20models%20and%20integrating%20advanced%20load%20management%20features%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20issues%20with%20many%20common%20charging%20stations%20in%20India%20is%20their%20inability%20to%20cater%20to%20different%20vehicle%20models%20and%20their%20battery%20specifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20the%20charger%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Vivek%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%2060kW%20DC%20Fast%20Charger%20converts%20AC%20power%20from%20the%20grid%20into%20DC%20power%20using%20an%20internal%20rectifier%20(AC%2FDC%20converter).%20It%20delivers%20high-power%20DC%20output%20directly%20to%20the%20battery%2C%20bypassing%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20onboard%20charger%20for%20quicker%20energy%20transfer.%20The%20charger%20communicates%20with%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20Battery%20Management%20System%20(BMS)%20to%20determine%20the%20required%20charge%20level%20and%20adjusts%20the%20power%20output%20dynamically.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20Vivek%20also%20explains%20some%20of%20its%20key%20specifications%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPower%20Output%3A%2060kW%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInput%20Voltage%3A%C2%A0%20340-480V%20AC%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOutput%20Voltage%20Range%3A%20100V%20%E2%80%93%201000V%20DC%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEfficiency%3A%2095%25%2B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOperating%20Temperature%3A%20-20%C2%B0C%20to%20%2B50%C2%B0C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EComponents%20and%20standing%20apart%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Components%20of%20the%20DC%20Fast%20Charger%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERectifier%20(AC%2FDC%20Converter)%3A%20Converts%20incoming%20AC%20power%20to%20DC%20power%20for%20faster%20battery%20charging.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECooling%20System%3A%20An%20advanced%20air%20or%20liquid%20cooling%20system%20ensures%20the%20charger%20operates%20at%20safe%20temperatures%20during%20high-power%20operation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProprietary%20Controller%20Card%3A%20Manages%20real-time%20operations%2C%20safety%20protocols%2C%20and%20communication%20with%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPower%20Filters%3A%20Ensure%20clean%2C%20stable%20power%20output%20by%20reducing%20noise%20and%20harmonics%2C%20enhancing%20overall%20charger%20performance.